name: Quick Sync
description: Quick Sync offers a privacy-first, decentralized space to share, build, and monetize, without middlemen, centralized servers, or surveillance. With proprietary decentralized infrastructure, Zero-Knowledge encryption, and Web3 APIs, Quick Sync puts power back where it belongs: To people. QS Ecosystem consists of 3 main products: - QS Share: Share files & collaborate privately. No middlemen, no surveillance. - QS Build: Create your OWN privacy-first apps. No-code? No problem. - QS Marketplace: Monetize your creativity on your terms.
